---
title: Crispy Chili-Roasted Tofu with Sugar Snap Pea Sofrito & Fresh Mint
description: Almost every culture has its own blend of aromatic vegetables that make up a “sofrito” – our version uses carrot, onion, celery, and sweet bell pepper to give this dish its flavor base. A combination of both soft and crunchy veggies gives this dish textural pizazz, while spicy roasted tofu adds zip. A little fresh mint over top wakes up all the flavors!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5556145e4dab71c4718b4568.
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/5556145e4dab71c4718b4568.pdf
